    <entry>
      <title>游戏Minecraft电脑版如何更换窗口图标</title>
      <link href="posts/6/"/>
      <url>posts/6/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="1"><a href="#1" class="headerlink" title="1."></a>1.</h3><p>打开游戏根目录，打开.minecraft文件夹</p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/04201aa355e983aed36a2b9968efe07815316910.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><h3 id="2"><a href="#2" class="headerlink" title="2."></a>2.</h3><p>打开assets文件夹，进去后打开indexes文件夹</p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/586bfdefe07814319f0b40dfdc6699cf03536210.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/988e1c532f632385a78b9022cce833e038725d10.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><h3 id="3"><a href="#3" class="headerlink" title="3."></a>3.</h3><p>打开到这里，会发现后很多后缀名为json的文件</p><p>而且这些文件的命名都是以minecraft的游戏版本命名的（例如：1.7.10.json，1.8.9.json）</p><p>用文本编辑软件打开相应版本的文件</p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e3d059e833e0397271bec959b586304860435610.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><h3 id="4"><a href="#4" class="headerlink" title="4."></a>4.</h3><p>利用软件的查找功能，大多数的快捷键都为Ctrl+F</p><p>分别查找icon_16x16和icon_32x32 </p><p>找到后，复制 “hash”：“这里面的字符”</p><p>16x16大小的有一串字符，32x32大小的有一串字符，都要记住</p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/6002c9d4483104eba21a2dbc092b74ee1d324e10.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/75af02324b18512cd74caa14ad334884cce34910.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/cca2552c56ee7b7fe5b30ec66ef4fcf5ef0d4110.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><h3 id="5"><a href="#5" class="headerlink" title="5."></a>5.</h3><p>回到游戏根目录，打开.minecraft文件夹中的assets</p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/fdb4f00d3aceaad718d67e51eee7340f6578b810.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><p>之后打开里面的objects，并找到那两串数据开头前两个字符命名的两个文件夹</p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/64a62a0f64781423ce04048daac2bbd6e0d0b210.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/9b2098254193cee8cab926a85a0ff2260c9aa810.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/0cdb2f0e1799e92a380530f3e1fec314f0c5a010.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><p>分别打开这两个文件夹，找到以那两串数据命名的文件</p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/f0848bee41c1b72726ee743b1a2ca5cadde89810.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/01bd69f7980e5f20d7cc2d68bd20b93acc898e10.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><p>分别把这两个文件的名字加上后缀.png</p><p>打开后就会发现里面是我的世界原版的图标。</p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/589f5b078801387074fc483f2d08a50f95fc8310.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><p><img src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/8b3643dd884ce54a829a955ca3066b0193ddf710.jpg?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_500,limit_1"></p><p>之后我们做两个分别是16x16,32x32的图标替换进去，去掉.png的后缀名</p><h3 id="6"><a href="#6" class="headerlink" title="6."></a>6.</h3><p>最后我们的minecraft客户端自定义图标就完成了</p><h3 id="声明"><a href="#声明" class="headerlink" title="声明"></a>声明</h3><p>此文章最早是我发布在百度经验上的</p><p>因为是一年前写的了，所以我本地已经没有了图片文件</p><p>所以是用的百度经验的图片</p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 教程文章 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
